# Frontend Patterns

## Components
- Use shadcn/ui primitives from src/components/ui/ as base.
- Compose domain components in src/components/trips/, hotels/, flights/, places/.
- No inline styles. Tailwind only.
- Export one component per file (named export, not default).

## Forms
- react-hook-form with zodResolver.
- Use FormField, FormItem, FormLabel, FormControl, FormMessage pattern.
- Validate on submit, not on blur (better UX for first-time fill).

## Data fetching
- Use TanStack Query hooks (src/hooks/) in Client Components.
- Prefer Server Components + direct Supabase server client for initial loads.
- Invalidate queries after mutations, not manual cache updates (except Realtime).

## Realtime
- Subscribe via src/hooks/use-realtime.ts.
- On INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE events, call queryClient.setQueryData() or queryClient.invalidateQueries().
- Unsubscribe in useEffect cleanup.

## Accessibility
- All interactive elements have aria labels or visible text.
- Use Radix UI primitives for keyboard navigation.
